WEBVTT

00:00.010 --> 00:01.665
Previously on "Mr. Mercedes"...

00:01.666 --> 00:03.795
I would've thought she'd be back by now.

00:03.796 --> 00:06.709
She didn't even pack up
her shit. Not even a note.

00:06.710 --> 00:09.959
- You really loved her.
- I just don't get it.

00:09.960 --> 00:11.759
My focus is whether you'll be able

00:11.760 --> 00:14.219
to contribute meaningfully
to your own defense.

00:14.220 --> 00:16.079
Uh, yeah.

00:16.079 --> 00:18.079
Ms. Linklatter, you have
been found competent.

00:18.080 --> 00:19.769
It is therefore your legal right

00:19.770 --> 00:21.604
to have your day in court.

00:21.605 --> 00:23.732
"With public sentiment on one's side,

00:23.733 --> 00:25.229
nothing can fail."

00:25.230 --> 00:26.692
Brady say that, did he?

00:26.693 --> 00:28.499
The public is gonna set me free.

00:28.500 --> 00:30.019
I got a high school
buddy, Andy Halliday,

00:30.020 --> 00:31.039
runs an old bookstore.

00:31.040 --> 00:32.719
Well, some kid came into the bookstore

00:32.720 --> 00:35.379
asking about Rothstein... that kid!

00:35.380 --> 00:37.159
That's the Saubers family.

00:37.160 --> 00:39.239
Pete, we got another
envelope this morning.

00:39.240 --> 00:40.659
$9,000.

00:40.660 --> 00:41.999
Where'd you get the money?

00:42.000 --> 00:43.209
It's not coming from me.

00:43.210 --> 00:44.419
May I ask a question?

00:44.420 --> 00:45.959
Are we on a date?

00:45.960 --> 00:47.089
Would you like it to be?

00:48.040 --> 00:50.629
Everybody I touch suffers.

00:50.630 --> 00:52.599
You're really worried about her, Lou.

00:52.600 --> 00:53.761
She's fucked.

00:53.762 --> 00:56.514
- My doing.
- Not everything is your doing.

00:56.515 --> 00:57.519
But this one is.

00:57.520 --> 00:59.726
I wanna call Holly as a witness.

00:59.727 --> 01:02.145
She could be a De facto surrogate.

01:02.146 --> 01:06.309
"If you like Holly,
wait till you see Lou."

