♪ What is this that I can't see ♪

01:24.720 --> 01:29.499
♪ With icy hands taking hold on me ♪

01:29.500 --> 01:32.619
♪ I am death and none can excel ♪

01:32.620 --> 01:37.219
♪ I'll open the doors
to heaven or hell ♪

01:37.220 --> 01:40.530
♪ Oh, death ♪

01:40.560 --> 01:42.999
♪ Oh, death ♪

01:43.000 --> 01:48.299
♪ Can't you spare me over
till another year? ♪

01:48.300 --> 01:50.959
- ♪ Oh, death ♪
- Give it up, Billy boy.

01:50.960 --> 01:54.199
- ♪ Oh, death ♪
- Throw in the towel.

01:54.200 --> 01:56.139
Okay?

01:56.140 --> 01:58.409
You don't have what it takes.

01:58.410 --> 01:59.499
You never did.

01:59.500 --> 02:02.279
♪ Someone would pray,
couldn't you call ♪

02:02.280 --> 02:03.869
You're not here.

02:03.870 --> 02:06.640
No. I'm dead.

02:07.940 --> 02:10.419
But clearly, not gone.

02:10.419 --> 02:13.940
And that's your fear, isn't it?

02:13.950 --> 02:18.179
Once you're dead, gone,
gone, gone, gone.

02:18.180 --> 02:22.739
But the fear that's under that one...

02:22.740 --> 02:27.146
let's call it, uh, totem pole fear...

02:27.147 --> 02:32.379
is that you were never
there in the first place.

02:32.380 --> 02:35.689
You got no legacy.

02:35.690 --> 02:40.069
You think finding my killer
is gonna give you one?

02:40.070 --> 02:42.099
Well, let me tell you something, bud.

02:42.100 --> 02:45.139
Legacy is shit.

02:45.140 --> 02:47.960
And shit don't mean shit.

