34:10.710 --> 34:14.899
Oh, my God. Satan's a human creation.

34:14.900 --> 34:19.399
He's like God or Cheez
Whiz, or, you know...

34:19.400 --> 34:21.998
Billy, I think you're missing the point.

34:22.000 --> 34:24.899
There's only one way out,

34:24.900 --> 34:27.190
