37:17.570 --> 37:20.019
I'm a little uneasy.

37:20.020 --> 37:24.960
I'm gonna be sounding real
good when I'm out, though.

37:26.000 --> 37:27.939
She's getting worse.

37:27.940 --> 37:30.939
And the way she talks is
how Brady would talk.

37:30.940 --> 37:33.959
