spoke with Brady, you know.

37:33.960 --> 37:36.289
I did. You're not wrong.

37:36.290 --> 37:38.990
He's in her head somehow.

37:40.080 --> 37:41.339
What do we do?

37:41.340 --> 37:44.539
First of all, whatever
we can to get her out.

37:44.540 --> 37:47.089
