37:49.850 --> 37:51.919
I just wanted to say a quick thank you.

37:51.920 --> 37:53.159
My name's Morris Bellamy.

37:53.160 --> 37:55.219
I was at the jobs fair that night...

37:55.220 --> 37:57.119
one of the lucky ones.

37:57.120 --> 37:58.609
Hello.

37:58.610 --> 38:01.160
Hi.

38:01.170 --> 38:04.639
So many of us are so
grateful to both of you.

38:04.640 --> 38:07.779
And I'm not sure it
gets said quite enough,

38:07.780 --> 38:09.279
so I thought I'd say it.

38:09.280 --> 38:12.519
- Thank you.
- Thank you, both of you.

38:12.520 --> 38:14.960
Again, sorry to intrude.

38:17.480 --> 38:19.710
Wait just a second.

38:22.500 --> 38:25.660
You were one of Brady
Hartsfield's victims?

38:27.540 --> 38:30.659
Well, emotionally.

38:30.660 --> 38:32.939
I escaped physical harm.

38:32.940 --> 38:34.979
Thank God.

38:34.980 --> 38:38.139
Where's your head at on this?

38:38.140 --> 38:39.339
I'm sorry?

38:39.340 --> 38:40.559
This trial. Do you want to see

38:40.560 --> 38:42.863
Lou Linklatter convicted or set free?

38:45.470 --> 38:48.539
Lou Linklatter's a hero in my book.

38:58.620 --> 39:01.489
Did you have an opportunity
to speak with her after?

39:01.490 --> 39:02.499
I did.

39:02.500 --> 39:05.359
And did she tell you where she
procured the 3-D revolver?

39:05.360 --> 39:06.759
She told me she made it herself.

39:06.760 --> 39:08.012
Is that easy to do?

39:08.013 --> 39:09.338
No. There's a fair amount

39:09.339 --> 39:11.199
of engineering expertise involved.

39:11.200 --> 39:12.259
Premeditation.

39:12.260 --> 39:15.059
Coherent thinking. Malice aforethought.

39:15.060 --> 39:17.819
That was all part of the
mix of what you observed,

39:17.820 --> 39:19.119
was it not, Mr. Montez?

39:19.120 --> 39:21.979
- Objection, foundation.
- Lay opinion.

39:21.980 --> 39:23.194
Move it along.

39:24.420 --> 39:27.979
As you observed the defendant
shoot Brady Hartsfield,

39:27.980 --> 39:29.899
she appeared to be acting calmly,

39:29.900 --> 39:31.411
willfully, and with purpose?

39:31.412 --> 39:32.459
Appeared to be the case.

39:32.460 --> 39:35.539
And was Brady Hartsfield
posing a threat to anybody

39:35.540 --> 39:39.119
when Lou Linklatter
acted to end his life?

39:39.120 --> 39:40.779
No.

39:40.780 --> 39:42.629
She executed him.

39:42.630 --> 39:44.699
Appeared to be the case.

39:44.700 --> 39:46.580
Thank you, Mr. Montez.

39:55.640 --> 39:57.259
You swore to tell the truth.

39:57.260 --> 39:59.219
I did.

39:59.220 --> 40:03.079
But you have an even higher obligation

40:03.080 --> 40:04.179
to tell it, don't you?

40:04.180 --> 40:07.349
You're a prosecutor,
an officer of the court.

40:07.350 --> 40:09.532
My obligation is the same
as any other witness.

40:09.533 --> 40:11.579
As an Ohio prosecutor,

40:11.580 --> 40:14.787
do you know and understand
Ohio criminal law?

40:14.788 --> 40:16.529
Well, that would be the goal.

40:16.530 --> 40:19.159
Before the shooting, would you say

40:19.160 --> 40:22.819
Brady Hartsfield seriously
provoked my client?

40:22.820 --> 40:25.059
Not in court, not on that day.

40:25.060 --> 40:26.699
In the months leading up to the event,

40:26.700 --> 40:28.899
when he attacked her,
when he almost killed her,

40:28.900 --> 40:31.219
almost killed thousands of people,

40:31.220 --> 40:33.264
would you say he provoked her?

40:34.620 --> 40:36.179
That's fair.

40:36.180 --> 40:40.239
Did his provocation cause my client

40:40.240 --> 40:41.719
to suffer great mental

40:41.720 --> 40:43.879
or emotional distress, if you know?

40:43.880 --> 40:45.819
Cause her to fear for her life?

40:45.820 --> 40:49.289
Cause her to lose sleep, weight,

40:49.290 --> 40:51.189
hopes...

40:51.190 --> 40:54.819
I can't argue with any of that.

40:57.900 --> 41:00.749
A person in Ohio can't be convicted

41:00.750 --> 41:03.961
of both murder and manslaughter
for the same killing.

41:03.962 --> 41:05.879
No. It's one or the other.

41:05.880 --> 41:07.409
Because not all killings are the same.

41:07.410 --> 41:08.925
Murder is worse than manslaughter.

41:08.930 --> 41:12.999
