41:38.360 --> 41:40.829
No.

41:40.830 --> 41:45.139
Did you know how having
to give testimony

41:45.140 --> 41:46.670
would affect her that day?

41:49.120 --> 41:52.170
I didn't realize the extent, no.

41:52.177 --> 41:55.249
Do you make room for the
possibility, Mr. Montez,

41:55.250 --> 41:58.019
that having been assaulted
by Brady Hartsfield,

41:58.020 --> 42:00.559
nearly killed by him in
the most vicious way,

42:00.560 --> 42:03.429
being stabbed in the stomach, and then

42:03.430 --> 42:06.779
having to be in a room with
him to face him down...

42:06.780 --> 42:08.819
do you make room for
the possibility that

42:08.820 --> 42:13.199
it was just all too much
for Lou Linklatter?

42:13.200 --> 42:14.860
Is it possible?

42:17.710 --> 42:20.440
Of course it's possible.

42:22.280 --> 42:24.470
Thank you.

42:27.590 --> 42:30.879
Calm, coherent,

42:30.880 --> 42:32.719
